<HEADLINE>
<P>
SARAH VAUGHAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
I remember one magical night in Agoura High School Gymnasium about 13 years 
ago. 
</P>
<P>
It was a school variety show and Sarah Vaughan sang for us. We were an audience 
of students, parents and teachers -- not a very large audience. Vaughan brought 
with her that night her own back-up musicians. 
</P>
<P>
It was a night my family and I will never forget. Thank you, Sarah. 
</P>
<P>
LILLIAN SAROIAN 
</P>
<P>
Woodland Hills 
