<TEXT>
<P>
Sarah Vaughan is prematurely dead of cigarette smoking, hard on the heels of 
Lucille Ball and Ava Gardner. My sadness at the Divine One's passing is tinged 
with anger that a singer blessed with such a magnificent voice could destroy it 
-- and herself -- with nicotine addiction. 
</P>
<P>
MARVIN H. LEAF 
</P>
<P>
Rancho Mirage 
