<P>
Photo, Dodgers Alfredo Griffin (7) and Willie Randolph collide at second trying 
to retire Roberto Alomar in eighth inning. Throw went into right field, and 
Alomar later scored. VINCE COMPAGNONE / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
