awareness of AIDS through music and education. The performers will do versions 
of Cole Porter songs in the 90-minute show, which will be broadcast on 
television and made into a video. "Red, Hot and Blue" will be broadcast Dec. 1 
on ABC in the United States. GREG BRAXTON 
